OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisney elects woman as     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchairman for first time in 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F98-year history            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Walt Disney has elected a woman to     
OL,6, become its chairman for the first time 
OL,7, in the entertainment giant's 98-year   
OL,8, history.                               
OL,10,FSusan Arnold, who has been a Disney    
OL,11,Fboard member for 14 years, will succeed
OL,12,FBob Iger at the end of this year.      
OL,14,FShe was formerly an executive at global
OL,15,Finvestment firm Carlyle.               
OL,17,FMr Iger, who stepped down as Disney's  
OL,18,Fchief executive in 2020 after 15 years 
OL,19,Fin the role, will leave the company by 
OL,20,Fthe end of this month.                 
